# Python Development Rules

Python-specific rules extend the universal development principles.

All AI agents working on Python-based projects must follow:

**📋 [.agents/rules/base.md](.agents/rules/base.md)**

and:

**📋 [.agents/rules/python-project.md](.agents/rules/python-project.md)**

## Compliance

Before starting Python work, agents must:
1. Read and understand `base.md`
2. Read and understand `.agents/rules/python-project.md`
3. Apply the Python-specific testing, typing, and design guidance there
